MODEL B — Two-button approach (cleaner)
   - "Pass to another agent" button
     → I can't do this, but property may still be valid
     → reassigns
   - "Reject listing" button  
     → Fundamental problem (fake docs, illegal property, scam)
     → status = 'rejected' immediately
     → landlord notified
     → no reassignment

