Admin-Report & Flag System
Report buttons on booking pages (tied to a specific tenancy/incident):
- student/booking.php: student can report agent or landlord
- landlord/booking.php: landlord can report student or agent
- agent/case.php + agent/inspection.php: agent can report landlord or student
Report in chat system:
- Right-click / long-press a specific message to report it
- Attaches the exact message as evidence for admin
- Catches misconduct before a booking exists (harassment, scam attempts in general inquiry chat)
All reports aggregate in admin dashboard with count, reason, and reporter identity.
High report count on a user triggers an alert so admin can investigate and suspend.

